Package org.opengis.cite.iso19136.components

package org.opengis.cite.iso19136.components
Includes tests to verify schema components that define specific types of geographic objects as required in clause 21.2.1 of ISO 19136.
"Any GML application schema shall be of at least one of the schema types described in 21.3 through 21.11, and comply to the rules from the respective Subclauses in addition to 21.2."
See Also:
